# ── QZ Tray request signing ────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Private key matching the certificate in client/src/lib/qz-certificate.ts.
# Used by POST /api/printing/qz/sign to sign every QZ Tray print request so
# the QZ Tray prompt no longer says "anonymous request / Untrusted website".
#
# SECURITY: NEVER ship this to the frontend. It must remain server-side only.
# Generate per https://qz.io/wiki/2.0-signing-messages and paste the contents
# of private-key.pem here on a single line with literal \n between PEM lines,
# OR replace this with a multi-line value if your hosting allows it.
# On Railway, set it as a Variable (not in this file).
QZ_PRIVATE_KEY="-----BEGIN PRIVATE KEY-----\nPASTE_PRIVATE_KEY_BASE64_HERE\n-----END PRIVATE KEY-----"
